                    <h2>Expenses</h2>
                    <p>Track and manage your expenses effectively. Review monthly reports and set budgets to stay on top of your spending.</p>
                    <a href="/expenses" class="view-details">View Details</a>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="feature-card">
                <div class="icon-container">
                    <i class="fas fa-piggy-bank"></i>
                </div>
