                    <h2>Savings</h2>
                    <p>Monitor your savings and set goals. Explore savings plans and track your progress towards financial goals.</p>
                    <a href="/savings" class="view-details">View Details</a>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="feature-card">
                <div class="icon-container">
                    <i class="fas fa-money-bill-wave"></i>
                </div>
                <div class="text-content">
                    <h2>Salary</h2>
                    <p>Keep track of your salary and earnings. Manage payroll, view payslips, and track income over time.</p>
                    <a href="/income" class="view-details">View Details</a>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="feature-card">
                <div class="icon-container">
                    <i class="fas fa-umbrella"></i>
                </div>
                <div class="text-content">
                    <h2>Insurance</h2>
                    <p>Manage your insurance policies and claims. Access policy details, file claims, and review coverage options.</p>
                    <a href="/insurance" class="view-details">View Details</a>
